  "Description": {
    "English": "A strange, shifting map. Though hard to focus upon, this chart appears to show the location of a nearby <span class=\"name name-special\">Sentinel Pillar</span>. Such Sentinel strongholds house many secrets...<br><br>Select the map and use <VAL_ON>Plot Route (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> to pin the location in your Exosuit display.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一张奇异的、不断变化的地图。尽管很难聚焦，这张地图似乎显示了附近<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫之柱</span>的位置。这样的护卫据点守护者无数秘密......<br><br>选择地图并使用<VAL_ON>规划路线（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）<>以在你的套装屏幕中标记该地点。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一張奇怪、不斷變化的地圖。雖然很難集中注意，不過這張圖似乎顯示了附近的<span class=\"name name-special\">巡警台柱</span>。這類巡警要塞隱藏著許多秘密......<br><br>選擇地圖並使用<VAL_ON>規劃路線 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<>，即可在你的強化套裝顯示中釘選該地點。"
  },
